OL,3,GWales
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FLow cloud clearing during the
OL,6,Fmorning. A very warm day follows with
OL,7,Fplenty of strong sunshine, though
OL,8,Fcloud may push into the far north.
OL,9,FLight winds.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FSome patchy cloud in the
OL,12,Fnorth but clearer in the south. Mist
OL,13,Fand fog may develop in places. Light
OL,14,Fwinds and feeling mild.
OL,15,
OL,16,CWednesday:FAny mist and fog will lift
OL,17,Fquickly, leaving a bright and sunny
OL,18,Fday for all. Feeling hot in the strong
OL,19,Fsunshine, especially in the east.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
